{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139840/extras/About_the_Game_628_x_182_bright.gif?t=1738266422\" />Assume the role of Derek Ericona, a lord destined for death by treachery, who avoided it in favor of a more grim fate. You're in for a great adventure inspired by games like Castlevania and Dark Souls.  Bloodthirsty monsters, divine creatures and epic boss battles. The game\u2019s story is shaped by  choices that will define your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Metroidvania</strong> - Unlock unique upgrades for movement and combat to expand the world. Maintaining the game's progression requires you to use different relics, items and abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenging bosses</strong> - Test your skills against multiple bosses and other creatures from the Dark Ages. The game will constantly test your patience as you face challenging battles that require their own unique approach.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combat galore</strong> - You must use an ever-expanding arsenal of weapons and equipment to repel  a wide variety of enemies. Put your courage, skills, and resolve on display for them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration</strong> - The game features a huge world represented by a variety of hand-crafted levels. From fog-shrouded ruins, where undead corpses cling to any living being passing by, and shambling figures emerge. To the Sun-city that hides in the labyrinthine of an ancient tomb where an unspeakable evil lingers, long forgotten by mankind.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Non-linear exploration</strong> \u2013 Play through levels and bosses, discover side areas with more secrets and enemies to defeat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Weapons and Equipment</strong> \u2013 Your character can be armed with bows, scythes, longswords, whips, pistols, rifles, and many more traditional weapons. More exotic weapons will also be available to you, so use any means to achieve success.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple Endings</strong> \u2013 Make key decisions along the way to determine Ericona's fate as you progress through the story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/913be7b5b93c43bbb6d42b79b316fdcb494875ac.jpg"},{"name":"Mushroom Slaver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/c2f73674ea52f76a7e02846bca66d0f9efd00e6f.jpg"},{"name":"Devourer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/3e1439b9d5b1d79bf4cd61d66fd94b87f5228e71.jpg"},{"name":"Ghul the Jailer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/a18cbf6d5eeecbc3688fbd3a811a0ffcb6df1a44.jpg"},{"name":"Mother of the Pack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/45bc3081070882106fb06d65382fa23d026b6a3b.jpg"},{"name":"Violence of the Judgement","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/a5b546e6c98a3a7a0a93a2b33c90cfdbb99badae.jpg"},{"name":"1'st Archon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/bd01cacfab338c20499f262cea344a2377f499ec.jpg"},{"name":"Great Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/2ea7dadfe894770d1aab231f1a1ede567d8fada7.jpg"},{"name":"Winged Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/59a0a4b4f43d2bdf166c301146e10164aa54f337.jpg"},{"name":"Thunder in the sky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139840/